Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第三界层的沙漠世界\N展开了旅程的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入了由剑作支配的火热村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为太热\N令武一郎师傅倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外勇者之剑也被偷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我不能叫龙神丸出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过全靠火美子把剑找回来\N让我打倒了剑作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了找出令第三界层\N恢复原状的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由火热村出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.37,0:02:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十二话\N玛利亚妮的火烧记念日!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.87,0:02:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒、朱古力芭菲、苏打水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了\N你令我越来越口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.92,0:02:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了\N不论走多久也没有任何线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只令我热得不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.33,0:02:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的热度\N就算是我也支持不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能理解的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真没用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了,大人是风之子\N小孩是火之子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好像有点错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨!我看见那边有些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪糕啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难理解的家伙们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个热气是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比起沙漠更热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是多恶达手下的城吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N但是个从未见过的种类呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看来有点太轻敌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再继续\N让他们成功下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样也要在这第三界层\N收拾他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚妮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样\N可以打倒渡他们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无论怎样也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!到了午后沐浴的时间了\N对不起,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!古拿玛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚妮大人\N我有消息给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接说了\N渡他们已到了这条村附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.93,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是时候\N让他们见识你的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.11,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起\N因为有不清洁的虫在飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只是想消毒一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.74,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消毒吗?\N倒是你打算怎样对付渡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.27,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要引他进这个城吗?\N还是要在灼热的地面上烧熟他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢…呀!是了\N你可以引他们来澡室吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这么热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N整条村便像铁板烧一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是方便的地面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样住在这里的人\N会受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连在地面上走动也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是火美子她真慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来从刚才起\N便看不见她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时她都会是最先来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子\N她到底打算干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法,从天空拜访之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是污穢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐非常喜欢清洁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要少许不清洁\N我也会很不高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.82,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为想村民们也清洁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把地面弄热来个全体消毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!差不多是到了\N午后的超热时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超热时间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别超热时间,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子她没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,没有办法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下很怕热的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎样才…对了,可以用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊,这样飞过来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢\N古拿玛!快去救渡他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是要人照顾的家伙\N快点抓住我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢…蠢材!\N不要一次过这么多人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N这样不清洁的东西便没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领村内清洁\N姐姐真是个非常好的孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很烫呢\N真是个过分的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应是我说才对!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起,但是为什么\N地面突然全热起来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天午前和午后都会有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玛利亚妮大人令温度上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚妮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是支配着这条村的\N多恶达的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.40,0:08:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有异常的洁癖\N把全村的温度上升做全体消毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全村做全体消毒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时是很温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一看见不洁的东西\N性格便会改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.42,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?这样的话\N火美子她没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身是沙一点也不清洁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事件了,要快点去救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,我找到好东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是城内有事联络的声音放送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.36,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛先生\N你去了哪里?古拿玛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是玛利亚妮大人的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她为什么\N会认识古拿玛的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个…\N我们以前曾经碰过面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,我要你帮我\N快点来,古拿玛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,一定是引我去\N然后把我收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我反过来潜进去收拾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么也开不了\N不知怎办好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧\N谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你只是为了这样\N而叫我来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛先生\N你可以静一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生也是\N为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!\N你和我一样是来玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是非常有趣的地方啊\N我十分喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊!\N知道她是谁吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道?\N她是我们非打倒不可的渡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐,来玩吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我不管了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是武一郎流踩高晓之术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在村中\N有踩高晓王之称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点名气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,快点吧\N我很担心火美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,烧着了,赶快点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗?让他们进入城\N和玛利亚妮打一场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!这边啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧\N火美子被玛利亚妮捉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在遇到很可怕的事\N快点去救她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负这么可爱的少女\N真不能饶恕,去吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽不知那算不算是可爱\N总之上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是玛利亚妮也好\N这么肮脏的人进入了她的城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会就此算数的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩捉迷藏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,你在干什么?\N和我一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,火美子你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子她去了哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚妮大人\N渡他们潜进这个城来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们把这个城\N弄得很肮脏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,把泥弄得四处都是\N真是非常肮脏的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.90,0:12:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…不…不能饶恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子…你在哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵捉贼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道厉害了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我玩得这么高兴\N你在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.22,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩?是吗?\N遇上了太可怕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令你神经失常了呢…真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傻瓜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.49,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢这里\N我还要在这里玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子去了哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便是渡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婶婶你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婶婶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婶婶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是婶婶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然得干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.59,0:14:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢弄脏我的城\N而且还叫我婶婶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么婶婶你便是玛利亚妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又叫了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的婶婶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,在下怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美,真是美丽的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,你没有受伤吧\N来,抓住在下的手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,她便是玛利亚妮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大冒险呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,你竟用这么肮脏的手\N碰我的身体?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不能饶恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,你又摸了她\N一些奇怪的地方吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下没有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!这边啊,见到你太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,出口在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分两路来逃比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武一郎和火美子这边\N渡和我走这边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着到玛利亚妮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到哪里去了?快出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚妮大人\N渡逃到中庭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.14,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点用魔神收拾他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,我不会让你回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?出口在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道反抗我\N有什么后果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出了一身汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该\N接受弄脏我城堡的处罚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,玛利亚妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无礼,定是想我杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己在破坏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,我也没出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城堡啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.12,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟这样做…这样的话\N我要把你们全部杀掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎龙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么力量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能待在这里了\N在下也要快呼叫战神丸来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战…神…丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,战神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?感冒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不好呢,烧到多少度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这处是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很肮脏的婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是干这种事的时候\N虽不知你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.49,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你救我出来吧\N我是玛利亚妮大人的奶妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马? 奶妈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐是欺负我的可怕姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.12,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的!\N她本来是个非常温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被多恶达那家伙\N赐予了邪恶之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.55,0:19:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一天忘记了洗澡\N便说我不洁把我困在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那时侯起\N已有20年没有洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得这么臭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,把我救出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,我用忍法救你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完了,龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.16,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,不封住这电刀的话\N会被干掉的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙牙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我的火炎棍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我不想这样子输掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么样子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,又是那部魔神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.57,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.12,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这处交给战神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛武一郎流交叉字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?已打完了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我还把感冒\N的战神丸叫来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不热了,不热了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.83,0:21:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画像自古开始\N已在这城堡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.08,0:21:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N是有所分别的,但现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都在燃烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是\N有是什么奇怪的事发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.65,0:21:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个灼热地狱之迷\N也许便在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N的所在地在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以很清楚\N恐怕是在…


